You'll probably find that's due to the stupid PC software industries
tendency to make up their own standards.  Tell it you don't want to log on
as anonymous and put in "anonymous" as your user-name and
"whatever@the.hell.your.email.is", and make sure you're connecting to
de.aminet.net and not wuarchive.wustl.edu

