Hi Curt,

>What I'm doing is loading sound samples, and reading the iff header to
>determine the playing time for each sample.  This is returned as seconds,
>since samples always play at the same speed, regardless of VBlank rate.
>
>Then I use this information to know how long to disable the music on a
sound
>channel while the sound is playing, and turn it back on when the sound is
