It`s a pity your not playing the music samples using the audio device, as
then you can just send requests with higher prioritys and the audio device
sorts it all out, ie, you could have music playing, and then a long sample
starts, and in the middle of that a smaller sample with a higher priority
cuts in, and then returns to the long sample and after that the music ;),
but then I love devices ;)

Dave


