Neil Bullock churned out *this* drivel:

> Can someone tell me how to get Blitz to check for the exitstence of a
> drive or assign without a requester appearing asking you to insert the
> drive?

Not sure, but I /think/ Lock_() works... 

Also, there's a little bit of text on page 111 of the manual under Exists
which might help...

See ya,
