2.  Is there a rule of thumb with a non-proportional font to estimate
how wide a column should be for a given number of characters?   I
don't really want to make it the width of umpteen W characters (or
whatever the widest would be).   The only thing I can think of would
be to adjust the column widths on the fly, sort of like MUI.

