Subject: Re: Gadtools gadgets again



> I'm still working on replacing standard gadgets with GT ones :-)
> I would like to remove gadget.library from executable but I'm still usin=
g
> two functions from it: REDRAW and ACTIVATESTRING. How to replace these
> instructions by OS calls? Any examples are welcome.

RefreshGList_ GTGadPtr(gtl,id),Peek.l(Addr Window(win)),0,1

ActivateGadget_ GTGadPtr(gtl,id),Peek.l(Addr Window(win)),0


