@NODE "Mail_283" "Re: Get RGB info"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Fri, 7 May 1999 03:51:37 +0000
Date: Fri, 07 May 1999 13:57:25 +1200
From: Julian Kinraid <jkinraid@clear.net.nz>
X-Accept-Language: en-GB,en
Subject: Re: Get RGB info
Encoding: 7bit

Andrew Guard wrote:
> 
> Can any of you tell me how to get RGB Vaules from this source.

DEFTYPE.ColorWheelHSB cwHSB   ; HSB Structure
DEFTYPE.ColorWheelRGB cwRGB   ; RGB Structure

; Put the Hue/Saturation/Brightness settings from the colourwheel
; into cwHSB
GetAttr_ #WHEEL_HSB, *wheel, &cwHSB

; Convert HSB to Red/Green/Blue
ConvertHSBToRGB_ &cwHSB, &cwRGB

; Now you can use cwRGB\cw_Red, cwRGB\cw_Green and cwRGB\cw_Blue

--
Julian Kinraid ....... jkinraid@clear.net.nz ....... ICQ:17257217

