@NODE "Mail_315" "Re: GT-Palette Requestor"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Sat, 8 May 1999 19:26:27 +0100
From: "Linda Bell" <zalda@home4968.freeserve.co.uk>
Subject: Re: GT-Palette Requestor
Date: Sat, 8 May 1999 19:22:43 +0100




>I am trying to make my own Palette requestor, I do not what to use
>GTPalette at all because I won't do what I want it to.


What is it that you don`t like about the palette requestor - might give me a
better idea of how to achieve your aims.

VICTOR BELL




