@NODE "Mail_321" "Re: GtList"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Tue, 25 May 1999 10:03:24 +0000
From: "David McMinn" <D.Mcminn@eee.rgu.ac.uk>
Organization: The Robert Gordon University, E&EE
Date: Tue, 25 May 1999 10:01:40 +0100
encoding: Quoted-printable
Subject: Re: GtList

> but when I try to put a GTbutton dynamicaly in this Window after the
> AttachGTlist, it don't work. What is the solution.

You can't do that. You would probably need to do this when you wanted to a=
dd 
the GTButton to the list:

DetachGTList 1
Free GTList 1
;
; remake entire GTList here, including new gadget
;
AttachGTList 1,1


