Organization: The Robert Gordon University, E&EE
Date: Tue, 18 May 1999 10:29:21 +0100
encoding: Quoted-printable
Subject: Re: GTShape relased?



> It's possible to leave GTShepe relased AFTER pressing it?
> (Some kind of toggle for GTShape with 2 images for press and relase)

You could set up a normal GTShape with two imnages and then change the 
activation flags to be a toggle type.

*g.Gadget=3DGTGadPtr(gtl,id)
*g\Activation=3D*g\Activation|#GACT_TOGGLESELECT

Might work.


