Hello!

I now that this might be answered on the list before as there was some talk
about MP3s, but didn't think I'd need any of that. But today a pal of mine
asked me about it and I thought of this discussion. So, the question is: how
can you find out (calculate) the play length (in seconds) of a MP3 file.

Regards,


Damir Arh


