Hello Malvin

Somewhere Malvin Wall wrote:
MW > How do you program so you can use the MUI prefs programs, so the user
MW > can change how my program looks?

You don't need to do nothing, by default you can change the GUI options just by
pressing the MUI button on the window. The only way to stop that would be to
disable the button...

