[=>> Does anyone know how you attach an object to another object seamlessly 
[=>> without a space.. IE, a PopFile gadget and a string ??
[=> 
[=> Another group tag, group the two objects like this
[=> 
[=> MUIKeyString 1,"",250,""
[=> MUIPopButton 2,#MUII_PopFile
[=> 
[=> MUIAddObjsHGroup 3,1,2
[=>    MUIAddTags 3,#MUIA_Group_Spacing,1
[=> MUICreateHGroup 3
[=> 
[=> The 1 stands for the number of pixels......1 is what you're looking for,
[=> it's normally 2 or 3

