Mine ain't got no greeny colour, as it's all set different from users
prefs.....but to add an image background to your groups add the following
tag to your group tags....

    MUIAddTags <group no,#MUIA_Background,#MUII_GroupBack

I don't think the #MUII_xxxx constants are in the doc, you'll have to look
in the c header file for the options available here....

