--BOUNDARY.272740208.3

Hello,

    Just thought I`d tell you all that I`ve uploaded the final version
of the screen2window blit example that has been flying round us for
a while to aminet. No doubt there are lots of bugs or cockups or summat,
but Simon has fixed if for GFX cards and I just changed the spare
rastport`s bitmap sizes..

It`s also attached to this mail :)

Cya!
-- 
<tsb>
<sb>*CONTACTING MWA:*
