@NODE "Mail_689" "Re: Speed assessment"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Thu, 13 May 1999 13:57:31 +0100
From: "Paul" <paulwest@stationone.demon.co.uk>
Organization: private
Date: 13 May 99 13:52:21 +0000
Subject: Re: Speed assessment
Encoding: 7bit

> [=>> This runs at 21-22 fps on my 040/25 (it was 25fps for 65 objects),
> [=>> as I added a few more for the 060 people. I expect an 060/50
> [=> 
> [=> It gave me 33.0492 FPS on 060/50 
> 
> 12.summat on my 030/40 :(((
> And it flickers horribly :(

Well its only an early nocked-up engine at the moment so its only
singlebuffered :-) I wouldn't expect it to be more than half speed a
high end 030 so that sounds about right.

-- 
Paul.

