Subject: Re: Two questions



> Simple two questions:
> 1. How can I change colours of GTButton text and background?
>     (GTSetAttrs with tags for GTText doesn't work...)

You can't. Not using standard methods anyway. You might want to try drawin=
g the 
graphics for the button in the colours you want then grabbing it as a shap=
e and 
using a GTShape.

> 2. What is the difference between Blitz Macros and Statements?

A macro is replaced directly in the code, by the code between Macro...End 
Macro. A statement is a separate function that has to be jumped to, and ha=
s its 
own variable space.


