Following up on Curt's idea, I've built the attached skeleton.   Can
anyone explain why the Boxf, written to 0,0,  appears in the right
place, but the text, written with BitMapPrint{} also to 0,0 goes down
at the bottom of the box?   I'm sure Im missing something easy, but
